    Cafe Luce, ristorante di passione

    Cafe Luce is a cozy Italian restaurant and wine bar in Midtown East Manhattan, offering fresh homemade pasta, seasonal salads, antipasti, and house-made desserts.

    Join us for weekend brunch, a refreshing Aperitivo Spritz, or a glass from our curated selection of Italian and international wines.

    Whether dining in, ordering takeout, or hosting a private event, Cafe Luce delivers an authentic Italian experience in the heart of NYC.

    235 E 53rd St, New York, NY (between 2nd & 3rd Ave)
    Open Daily | Lunch & Dinner | Brunch Sat–Sun 10am–4pm
    Delivery via Uber Eats, Grubhub & DoorDash
